definitions.definition: An inland county of England bordered by the English counties of Cheshire , Staffordshire , Worcestershire , Herefordshire and the Welsh county of Powys and county borough of Wrexham .
Shropshire Council , a local government unitary authority which replaced the county council in 2009 in all of Shropshire except Telford and Wrekin .

main_definition: An inland county of England bordered by the English counties of Cheshire , Staffordshire , Worcestershire , Herefordshire and the Welsh county of Powys and county borough of Wrexham .
secondary_definitions: Shropshire Council , a local government unitary authority which replaced the county council in 2009 in all of Shropshire except Telford and Wrekin .

definitions.definition: One of an English breed of black-faced hornless sheep similar to the Southdown , but larger.
